          %h2= t('pages.mission.sub_heading3')
          %p
            Studies indicate that in a flu season,
            %span{:style => "font-size:50px"} 50%
            %span= t('pages.mission.para4').html_safe
        .parent-daycare
          %h2= t('pages.mission.sub_heading4')
          %p= t('pages.mission.para5')
            
  .container.what-do-next
    .row
      .col-lg-12.col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12
        = image_tag 'mission_hand.png'
        %h2.what-do-next-heading
          What to do next:
          %br
            to mitigate risk in your facility,
            %br
              increase safety,
              %br
                and show you care.
        %p.wdnp At HSCA, our core mission is to assist you, the childcare operator, to nurture a healthy and safe environment for children and childcare workers. We seek to carry out this mission as we:
        %ul#mission-menu
          %li
            %a{:href => ""} 1. Outline risks
          %li
            %a{:href => ""} 2. Create community
          %li
            %a{:href => ""} 3. Set brenchmark
  #threestrep.container
    .row
      .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.out-ben
        .outline-risk
          %h2
            %span 1
            Outline risks
          %p Enlighten you about the serious and lesser-known health risks group care presents for children and their surrounding communities, and facilitate actionable, practical, easy-to-follow methods, procedures and tools…so you can practice the highest standard of infection prevention in your childcare environments—leading to healthier, happier children, staff, and parents.
        .benchmark
          %h2
            %span 3
            Benchmark
          %p Help accredited childcare facilities become a benchmark—and establish a new standard—by which healthier and safer childcare is measured and recognized.
      .col-lg-6.col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.community-area
        .community
          %h2
            %span 2
            Community
          %p Create a community of like-minded childcare operators who will help grow, promote and sustain a superior network of safe and health-preserving places for children to grow and be nurtured.
  #get-start-free.container
    .row
      .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-12.col-xs-12
        %p With our accreditation program, you’ll be a key component in a nationwide movement to create a higher standard for our children—and avoid debilitating sickness, harm and suffering… for your staff, the children under your care, and parents.
